data.description: All brick home in Keeneland Subdivision! This one story 4 bedroom, 2 bath home has 9ft ceilings, Hardwood floors in Foyer, FR DR, and Den, Kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, lots of cabinets, pantry, eat in bar plus nice size Breakfast Nook, all with tile floors, Split bedroom plan with 3 Bedrooms & bath on one side & MRBR, large walk in closet and bath on other side, nice size Utility Room with tile floors & lot of shelving, Den has a shiplap access wall, fireplace with gas logs, Crown molding in Foyer, Den & Dining Room,  walk out onto a huge deck with built in bench seating & 2 roll out awnings for those hot days, privacy fenced in back yard, fire pit, garden boxes, play center & picnic table, HVAC 12/2022, concrete driveway, lots of floored attic, oversized garage with raised storage, plus water softer system remains, HOA just $70 a year, beautifully landscaped, Close to schools, shopping and restaurants! A must see!
